        "meta_description": "Israel's new president-elect, Reuven \"Rubi\" Rivlin, is set to take the reins following seven years of leadership from Israel’s beloved President Shimon Peres. From the political party Likud, right-leaning Rivlin garnered 63 votes for the presidential seat on Tuesday, 10 more than Hatnua contender Meir Sheetrit. Peres called Rivlin on Tuesday evening to welcome him to the post. \"Rubi, Your Excellency the next President of the State of Israel, you are right for this role,” Peres told Rivlin. “It is a position that brings with it responsibility, you have to consider your every word and every action, but you will do it successfully because you are, to your core, a good person.”",
